        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_GAUGE_NAME": "暴击计量表",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_GAUGE_DESCRIPTION": "对白色部分造成<style=cIsDamage>70%</style>伤害,对蓝色部分造成<style=cIsDamage>250%</style>伤害。最大热量固定。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_NAME": "龙息",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_DESCRIPTION": "发射一道火焰光束,造成<style=cIsDamage>90%伤害</style>。离目标越近,点燃几率越高。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_NAME": "火球术",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热量。</style>发射一枚火球,命中时造成<style=cIsDamage>225%伤害并点燃</style>敌人。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_PUNCH_NAME": "零点爆炸",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_PUNCH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热量。</style>向前推进,引爆身后敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>。发射后立即撞击第一个敌人会在周围引发爆炸造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_FLAREGUN_NAME": "信号枪",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_FLAREGUN_DESCRIPTION": "发射一枚信号弹,在5秒内造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>,然后爆炸造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>,释放5枚信号弹各造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHIST_NAME": "受虐狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHIST_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热量。</style>被<style=cIsDamage>点燃</style>造成的伤害转化为<style=cIsHealing>治疗</style>,持续6.5秒。增加<style=cIsDamage>125%</style>攻击速度。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_NAME": "受虐狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_DESCRIPTION": "当达到<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>上限时,周期性地对自己造成伤害,以换取范围<style=cIsHealing>生命偷取</style>和灼烧。最多10秒后,<style=cIsDamage>引爆</style>,然后<style=cIsUtility>过热</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_SURGE_NAME": "怨恨",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_SURGE_DESCRIPTION": "当达到<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>上限时,你移动更快并获得<style=cKeywordName>双重射击</style>和<style=cIsHealing>生命偷取</style>。最多10秒后,<style=cIsDamage>引爆</style>,然后<style=cIsUtility>过热</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_SCEPTER_NAME": "但丁的斥责",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "发射一道强烈光束,造成<style=cIsDamage>140%伤害</style>。离目标越近,点燃几率越高。按住2秒或更久后,松开时发射一道最终光束,造成<style=cIsDamage>150%伤害</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_ANTICIPATION": "<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>每失去和/或获得100热量,纵火者获得1层预判;获得5层后,他可激活受虐狂;额外层数增加伤害和持续时间;所有层数在结束时消耗。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_DETONATE": "<style=cKeywordName>引爆</style>纵火者爆炸,造成<style=cIsDamage>150%伤害</style>乘以累积的预判层数。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_LIFESTEAL": "<style=cKeywordName>生命偷取</style>纵火者在受虐狂激活时回复造成伤害的<style=cIsHealing>18%</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_SURGE_LIFESTEAL": "<style=cKeywordName>生命偷取</style>纵火者在怨恨激活时回复造成伤害的<style=cIsHealing>5%</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_OVERHEAT_MASO": "<style=cKeywordName>过热:受虐狂</style>如果纵火者因热量积累过多而退出受虐狂,则应用EX过热,将其移动速度和伤害降低至70%。取消或让技能自然结束会应用过热,将其攻击速度降低至50%。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OVERHEAT_TEXT": "过热!",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_COOLING_TEXT": "冷却中...!",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OVERHEAT_EX_TEXT": "过热:EX!"
